WEBVTT

00:07:58.160 --> 00:08:01.176
as profane, impure, blasphemous,

00:08:01.200 --> 00:08:03.496
the wrong type of Islam,

00:08:03.520 --> 00:08:05.016
and their vision instead

00:08:05.040 --> 00:08:09.616
is a fantastical view
of cosmic apocalypse.

00:08:09.640 --> 00:08:10.976
It's a born again vision.

00:08:11.000 --> 00:08:14.416
Discard your past,
your society, your family and friends

00:08:14.440 --> 00:08:16.600
since they're all impure.

00:08:17.840 --> 00:08:20.320
Instead, become someone else,

00:08:21.240 --> 00:08:22.520
your true self,

00:08:23.480 --> 00:08:25.760
your authentic self.

00:08:27.000 --> 00:08:31.056
Now, this isn't
about a return to the past.